Song: Jodi Bhul Korei Bhul Madhur Holo
Ma Tui Amay Daya Korbi Ki Na Bol
Ei Kule Ami Aar Oi Kule Tumi
Jani Tomar Premer Jogyo Ami To Noi
Lalita Go Oke Aaj Chole Jete Bal Na
Ma Mago Ma Ami Elem Tomar Kole
O Amar Mon Jamunar Ange Ange
Mon Re Amar Hay Shunli Na
Coffee Houser Sei Addata Aaj Aar Nei
Ei Kshantuku Keno Eto Bhalo Lage
Bhab Kore Ki Sukh Paoa Jai
Rangini Kato Mon, Mon Dite Chay
Amay Chinte Keno Parchho Na Ma
Ta Bole Ki Prem Debo Na
Na Na Na Aaj Raate Aar
Ei Shahar Theke Aaro Anek Dure
E To Raag Noy Go E Je Abhiman
Ek Jhank Pakhider Mato Kichhu Roddur
Hridayer Gaan Shikhe To Gaay Go Sabai
Kathay Kathay Je Raat Hoye Jay
Ogo Barsha Tumi Jhoro Na Go
Ami Ajiban Shudhu Bhul Kore Gechhi
